description: Pet-friendly, highly upgraded 2-bedroom, 1-bath condo located in a full-amenity building in the heart of the South Loop. This southeast corner home showcases a custom kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. The spacious living and dining area is filled with natural light and offers beautiful city views. The luxurious stone bathroom features a double bowl vanity, and hardwood floors run throughout. Both bedrooms are generously sized with excellent closet space. Additional highlights include in-unit washer and dryer, a private balcony, and extra-large garage parking available.    The monthly assessment covers gas, heat, air conditioning, basic cable, and internet. The building offers full-service amenities, including a doorman and fitness center. Ideally situated near Grant Park, Museum Campus, CTA Red/Green/Orange Lines, Trader Joe's, Jewel-Osco, Mariano's, restaurants, and breweries.
